<plot>The hero of the film, Jeano, is a photographer and a cameraman who, like many artists during the recent economic transition, no longer had a chance to follow his vocation. Deprived of chance to continue making films, he is forced to do work that he feels is incompatible both with his soul and talent. He decides to change his life in an extraordinary way - he fakes his own death through the mass-media and leaves for the "paradise" of his childhood where he will stay forever...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?274990</url></doc>
